 drivers/hwtracing/coresight/coresight-etm4x-core.c        |   43 ++++++++++----
 drivers/hwtracing/coresight/coresight-etm4x.h             |    2 
 drivers/hwtracing/coresight/coresight-self-hosted-trace.h |   24 +++++++
